<h1>Вертикальный ритм на Compass</h1>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='date'>Thursday 01 May, 2014</span>
<span class='author'>by Ivan Samorodov</span>
</div>
<p>Create a vertical rhythm for your site by setting the <strong>$base-font-size</strong> and <strong>$base-line-height</strong> variables and then including the <strong>establish-baseline</strong> mixin at the root of your document.</p>
<div class="highlight sass"><table style="border-spacing: 0"><tbody><tr><td class="gutter gl" style="text-align: right"><pre class="lineno">1</pre><pre class="lineno">2</pre><pre class="lineno">3</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="nv">$base-font-size</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="m">16px</span>
<span class="nv">$base-line-height</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="m">24px</span>
<span class="k">@include</span> <span class="nd">establish-baseline</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table>
</div>

<h3>Mixins</h3>

<ul>
<li><strong>leader</strong>($lines, $font-size, $property)</li>
<li><strong>trailer</strong>($lines, $font-size, $property)</li>
</ul>

